sources.title: Code 207 | Full Movie | Hollywood Action | Jack Dimich
sources.description:
Code 207 - A criminal ring kidnaps women and sells them to wealthy clients. When they kidnap the wife of an ARMY Ranger, their plans change dramatically, when he finds the abandoned Prison where they are held. a deadly cat and mouse game begins as he hunts them while trying to save the women from being sold and shipped away.
2011.  Stars: Jack Dimich, Tino Struckmann, Todd Bush
